This artifact vendors the "brainstorming" skill from obra/superpowers.

Vendored files (upstream paths):
  - skills/brainstorming/SKILL.md
  - skills/brainstorming/spec-document-reviewer-prompt.md
  - skills/brainstorming/visual-companion.md
  - skills/brainstorming/scripts/{server.cjs,start-server.sh,stop-server.sh,helper.js,frame-template.html}

SKILL.md is ADAPTED, not verbatim. Patronus re-coupled it into its own lifecycle
(see docs/adr/0001-profiles-recouple-plugins-stay-as-is.md) with two additions:
an explicit ASCII-diagram step at design-presentation points, and a `grilling`
hand-off offered after design approval, before the spec is written. The body
otherwise follows upstream.

All other files above are copied verbatim. The scripts/ visual-companion server
was audited before shipping: it binds 127.0.0.1 by default, runs under umask 077
with per-session tokens, verifies a PID before signalling it on shutdown, and
makes no outbound network calls. It is launched by the agent on demand (with user
approval), never at install time.

